name: Guardian's Gala VIP Surprise Gift, Damaged
description:
As VIP treatment for ultra elite attendees of the YC121 Guardian's Gala, this gift box contains an extra-special surprise gift from the Angel Cartel.

It purportedly contains items of immense value but, in reality, can the Cartel really be trusted to leave such things unmolested?

This gift box seems to have suffered some damage in transit.
